The correction factors were evaluated considering

dependence of the gamma-ray detection efficiency on

the sample, and from the dead time.

x4freetext: The neutron capture gamma-ray spectra were obtained by
unfolding the observed capture gamma-ray pulse height
The unfolding program FERDOR yielded the upper and
lower values of gamma-ray spectrum, so a half of the
difference between the upper and lower values was
assumed to be the error of gamma-ray spectrum.
Uncertainties are not presented by author.
Data are on Fig.11 a of J,EPJ/A,50,55,2014.
